description.prev: {{KW:MAGIC}}: Give +1 {{HP}} to a random ally monster.

description.now: Add 3 random monsters costing 3 to your deck with +1/+1. Draw a card.
description.prev: Add 3 random monsters costing 3 or less in your deck with +1/+1. Draw a card.

description.now: {{KW:MAGIC}}: Give {{KW:TAUNT}} to all other monsters on the board.
Look at 3 random cards in your deck. Send one to the top of your deck with -2 {{COST}}.
description.prev: Look at 3 random cards in your deck. Choose one and add its copy to your hand with -2 {{COST}}.

description.now: Shuffle your hand into your deck. Draw 4 cards. They cost 1 less.
description.prev: Put your hand into your deck, shuffle it then draw 4 cards.

description.now: Deal 1 {{DMG}}. If it killed a monster, add a {{CARD:181|1}} to your hand. If it had >= 2 base {{HP}}, gain 1 {{GOLD}}.
description.prev: Deal 1 {{DMG}}. If this killed a monster, add {{CARD:181|1}} into your hand.

description.now: Deal a monster under {{KR}}'s {{ATK}} to your opponent and remove the {{KR}} (max 8 {{DMG}}).
description.prev: Deal a monster under {{KR}}'s {{ATK}} to your opponent and remove the {{KR}} (max {{DMG:10}}).

description.now: {{KW:MAGIC}}: Kill an ally monster and gain {{GOLD:2}}.
{{KW:MAGIC}}: Deal 2 {{DMG}} to an enemy monster or give +2 {{ATK}} to an ally monster.
description.prev: {{KW:MAGIC}}: Deal {{DMG:2}} and give +{{ATK:2}} to a monster.

description.now: Give an ally monster +1/+1, then deal its {{ATK}} as {{DMG}} to the monster in front of it.
description.prev: Deal selected ally monster's {{ATK}} as {{DMG}} to the monster in front of it and extra {{DMG}} to its owner (max: 6).

description.now: Add an {{CARD:10|1}}, {{CARD:9|1}} and {{CARD:31|1}} to your hand.
description.prev: Add a copy of a non DT paralysed monster to your deck. If used on ally monster, add it to the top of your deck.

description.now: {{KW:MAGIC}}: Look at 3 random starter cards. Add one to your hand and reduce its {{COST}} by 1.
description.prev: {{KW:MAGIC}}: Add 1 starter card to your hand. It costs 1 less.
Whenever an ally {{TRIBE:PLANT|1}} is summoned, gain +1/+1.

description.now: {{KW:MAGIC}}: Look at 3 random monsters in your Dustpile. Add one to your deck with +1/+1.
description.prev: {{KW:MAGIC}}: Look at 3 other random monsters in your dustpile and choose one. Add a copy of it to your hand.

description.now: {{KW:HASTE}}. {{KW:MAGIC}}: If played on the right side of the board, gain -3/-4, then summon an exact copy of this.
description.prev: {{KW:HASTE}}. {{KW:MAGIC}}: Summon an exact copy of this monster.

description.now: {{KW:TAUNT}}. {{KW:MAGIC}}: Look at 5 random monsters in your deck and choose one. Give it {{KW:TAUNT}}.
{{KW:TAUNT}}. {{KW:MAGIC}}: Kill all monsters with <= 2 {{HP}} and gain +2/+2 for each killed monster.
description.prev: {{KW:TAUNT}}. {{KW:MAGIC}}: Kill all monsters with a base {{COST}} <= 4 and gain +2/+2 for each killed monster.
